title: How a TikTok Star Ended Up in Prison
description:
Former TikTok Star Ali Abulaban aka JinnKidd murdered his wife and her friend. Olayemi Olurin explains what this reveals about abolition and the role misogyny plays in both the crime and the criminal system.
